membership:
The IAF is a member of the IUCN.  &#xd;
It is a signatory to the Memorandum of Understanding on Migratory Raptors.  &#xd;
It is an observer at the Bern Convention, the Convention on Migratory Species and CITES, among other organizations. &#xd;
It is an Advisory NGO to the Cultural Division of UNESCO.
